<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport">
	<title>Home | MyService</title>
	<link href="docs/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid">
	<noscript>
		<p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p>
	</noscript>
	<nav class="uikit-skip-link">
		<a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a>
	</nav>
	<% include ../global/partials/header-topbar-unauth.ejs %>

		<main>

			<section class="section-hero">
				<div class="container margin-below--extra" id="main-content">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-xs-offset-1 col-xs-10 col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8 col-lg-offset-3 col-lg-6">
							<img class="section-hero__logo" src="../../docs/images/myservice-logo-cobranded-stacked.svg" alt="The Department of Veterans' Affairs logo and MyService Beta logo appearing side by side"
							 title "Department of Veterans' Affairs - MyService Beta">
						</div>
					</div>

					<h1 class="section-hero__heading">A new way to claim</h1>
					<h2 class="section-hero__subheading">for current and former serving ADF members and&nbsp;their&nbsp;families</h2>

					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-5 col-lg-offset-2 col-lg-4">
							<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--block section-hero__btn" onclick="window.location.href = '/register'">
								<span class="section-hero__btn---text">Register for MyService</span>
							</button>
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-5 col-lg-4">
							<button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--block uikit-btn--mygov section-hero__btn" onclick="window.location.href = '/mygov-login'">
								<span class="section-hero__btn--text">Sign in with</span>
								<img class="section-hero__btn--image" src="../../docs/images/mygov-logo.svg" height="18" alt="myGov logo" title="Sign in with myGov">
							</button>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<div class="story pointing-block">
				<div class="pointing-block__top"></div>
				<div class="container">
					<div class="row story__section">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-offset-1 col-md-10">
							<h2 class="story__heading">MyService makes it easier for you to access DVA services&nbsp;online</h2>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="mys-grid">
						<div class="mys-grid__row story__section">
							<div class="mys-grid__cell">
								<h2 class="story__heading story__heading--left">Claiming made&nbsp;simple</h2>
								<p>
									<span class="heading heading--spacer"></span>
								</p>
								<ul class="story-points">
									<li>Apply for instant cover for mental health&nbsp;treatment</li>
									<li>Access support for a service-related condition&nbsp;or&nbsp;injury</li>
									<li>Apply for an increase in your disability&nbsp;pension</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
							<div class="mys-grid__cell">
								<img class="story__image" src="../../docs/images/hp-claims.png" alt="Image depicting the MyService claims page that includes the words Claim now for service-related injuries or illness, and a button to make claim."
								 title="Make a claim for service-related injuries or illness">
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="mys-grid__row story__section margin-below--extra">
							<div class="mys-grid__cell">
								<h2 class="story__heading story__heading--left">Easy access</h2>
								<p>
									<span class="heading heading--spacer"></span>
								</p>
								<ul class="story-points">
									<li>Access your digital DVA health&nbsp;card</li>
									<li>View your accepted conditions</li>
									<li>Track the status of your claims</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
							<div class="mys-grid__cell">
                <img class="story__image" src="../../docs/images/hp-healthcard.png" alt="Image depicting the MyService health card page that includes a digital version of a DVA white card" title="Access your DVA health card">
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

      </div>
				</div>
				<div class="pointing-block__bottom"></div>
			</div>

			<div class="story">
				<div class="container">
					<div class="row story__section">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 story__three-column">
							<img class="story__image story__image--small" src="../../docs/images/hp-listening.svg">
							<h2 class="story__heading story__heading--left">We're listening to you</h2>
							<p>
								<span class="heading heading--spacer"></span>
							</p>
							<p class="story__text">Tell us how your service-related conditions are affecting your life. This helps ensure you get the right support.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 story__three-column">
							<img class="story__image story__image--small" src="../../docs/images/hp-improvements.svg">
							<h2 class="story__heading story__heading--left">We're improving things</h2>
							<p>
								<span class="heading heading--spacer"></span>
              </p>
              <p class="story__text">While MyService expands, you will also have access to MyAccount (our old way of claiming online). If you are an existing MyAccount user, a MyService account has already
                been created for you. You can login here.</p>
							</p>
              <p class="story__text">We're still moving features across to MyService. In the meantime, you can move between MyService and MyAccount to access what you need.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 story__three-column">
							<img class="story__image story__image--small" src="../../docs/images/mygov-connect.svg">
							<h2 class="story__heading story__heading--left">We're linked to myGov</h2>
							<p>
								<span class="heading heading--spacer"></span>
							</p>
							<p class="story__text">Register for MyService then link your account to myGov. Once linked, use your myGov login details to access MyService.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>


		</main>
		<% include ../global/partials/footer.ejs %>




</body>

</html>
